### Create Playground Users
# Populates the database with a set of test users.
# Only available in local, dev, or test profiles.
# @name createUsers
POST {{host}}/api/playground/createUsers
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Expected Response (Success - 200 OK):
# { "status": "SUCCESS", "code": 0, "message": "Success" }


### Create Playground Media
# Populates the media store with test images.
